raw_data.title: Programmer
raw_data.description: Design, program, and implement Web-Based Trainings (WBT) and Internet and Intranet web-based applications. Responsible for the development of both front-end display code and back-end data management components.  WBTs are powered by an exclusive, proprietary software engine that is designed to be re-useable, and highly customizable to both the needs of the client and the needs of LMS platforms where the training will be hosted. All web-based applications and WBTs are compatible with all major web browsers and web server technologies. We ensure all websites and WBTs are compliant with current regulations and policies, and are 508 compliant. Our programmers are certified and have completed the Section 508 Trusted Tester certification program.
